attributes.Summary: This 5-stage, IP-only fabric design provides physical connectivity to 150 racks, and allows for expansion to as many as 210 racks (40.0% growth) in the future.

info.description: QFX5220 (hardware with base software), 128 QSFP+/QSFP28 ports, redundant fans, 4 AC power supplies, front-to-back airflow
